Class HostImplementation

java.lang.Object
neureka.backend.api.implementations.AbstractImplementationFor<HostCPU>
neureka.backend.standard.implementations.HostImplementation
All Implemented Interfaces:
ImplementationFor<HostCPU>
public class HostImplementation
extends AbstractImplementationFor<HostCPU>
This class is a wrapper class for the ImplementationFor<HostCPU> interface which enables a functional style of implementing the backend API!
It is used merely as a simple formality and implementation type specification. used to properly call a HostCPU instance via the ImplementationFor<HostCPU> lambda implementation receiving an instance of the ExecutionCall class.
